OL,5,Cshed
OL,7,FA jury at the Old Bailey has heard how
OL,8,Fwealthy aristocrat Constance Marten,
OL,9,F37, and her partner Mark Gordon, 49,
OL,10,Ffled authorities in January 2023 in an
OL,11,Fattempt to keep their newborn child
OL,12,Fafter four other children were taken
OL,13,Finto care.
OL,15,FThe pair were arrested in Brighton on
OL,16,F27 February 2023, two days before
OL,17,Ftheir daughter Victoria's decomposed
OL,18,Fbody was found inside a Lidl bag in a
OL,19,Fdisused allotment shed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
