OL,7,FThe cause of the child's death could
OL,8,Fnot be established.
OL,10,FThe jury found the couple guilty of
OL,11,Fconcealing the birth of a child and
OL,12,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,14,FThe couple had also faced charges of
OL,15,Fchild cruelty, manslaughter by gross
OL,16,Fnegligence and causing or allowing the
OL,17,Fdeath of a child, all of which they
OL,18,Fdenied.
