OL,7,FThe trial at the Old Bailey began on
OL,8,FJanuary 25. Jurors began deliberating
OL,9,Fon April 30 and were discharged after
OL,10,Fmore than 72 hours of deliberation.
OL,12,FJudge Mark Lucraft KC gave his
OL,13,F"sincere and heartfelt thanks" to
OL,14,Fjurors for their "truly exceptional"
OL,15,Fdedication.
OL,17,F"Please do not feel that you have
OL,18,Ffailed in any way," he said.
OL,20,FThe judge gave them the option of
OL,21,Flifetime exemption from jury service.
