OL,7,FOn Wednesday, prosecutor Tom Little KC
OL,8,Fannounced the Crown would seek a
OL,9,Fretrial as Judge Mark Lucraft KC
OL,10,Fallowed reporting of the two verdicts
OL,11,Ffollowing an application by PA news
OL,12,Fagency.
OL,14,FJudge Lucraft set a provisional six to
OL,15,Feight-week retrial from March 3 next
OL,16,Fyear.
