OL,7,FDetective Superintendent Lewis
OL,8,FBasford, Metropolitan Police, said:
OL,9,F"Following today's hearing before His
OL,10,FHonour Judge Mark Lucraft KC, I can
OL,11,Fnow confirm that Mark Gordon and
OL,12,FConstance Marten have been convicted
OL,13,Fof concealing the birth of a child and
OL,14,Fperverting the course of justice.
