OL,7,F"The jury could not reach a verdict
OL,8,Ffor both Mark Gordon and Constance
OL,9,FMarten on other charges and the
OL,10,Finvestigation team from the Met's
OL,11,FSpecialist Crime Command, alongside
OL,12,Four partners from the Crown
OL,13,FProsecution Service, will now prepare
OL,14,Ffor a re-trial in March 2025.
OL,16,F"We will not be making any further
OL,17,Fpublic statements until the conclusion
OL,18,Fof the re-trial.
