OL,7,FTwo days later, two officers uncovered
OL,8,FVictoria's badly decomposed body on a
OL,9,Fnearby allotment.
OL,11,FShe had been wrapped in a pink sheet
OL,12,Fand hidden beneath dirt and rubbish in
OL,13,Fthe Lidl bag.
OL,15,FThe defendants sat in the dock of the
OL,16,FOld Bailey for the hearing on
OL,17,FWednesday.
